{"tid":827853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【祝賀粉絲結婚】遭遇坎坷 無阻奇洛李維斯戥人高興","createTime":"2018-09-19T08:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T07:59:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"655d821b2d1f114ac44ccabe313963d9005621b4","tid":827853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180905/s00007/77d63f05e91bb6ae6cf07f206bd2bc4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180905%2Fs00007%2F77d63f05e91bb6ae6cf07f206bd2bc4e.jpg&h=704c4898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《殺神John Wick》奇洛李維斯（Keanu Reeves）感情生活坎坷；1999年，他當時的女友Jennifer Syme懷胎8月，女兒不幸夭折，兩年後Jennifer更因車禍身亡，終年28歲。此後奇洛再無公開過任何女友或感情生活；8年前，他形單隻影坐在公園長椅、神情哀傷的照片在網上瘋傳，惹來粉絲憐愛，並在facebook開設專頁「要讓奇洛快樂起來」，足見他的憂鬱形象深入民心。<br />\n<br />\n雖然奇洛李維斯命運坎坷，但他亦出名待人和善；據Us周刊報道，日前一對新人Leslie Walker和Jarrod Camara準備在加州灣區的Dream Inn舉行婚禮，Jarrod的伴郎卻在酒店的酒吧内發現奇洛李維斯蹤影，Jarrod的母親Darlette知道奇洛是兒子的頭號偶像，於是到酒吧邀請對方跟新郎新娘合照，沒想到奇洛一口答應，而且還擺出鬼馬又興奮表情，並做出搖滾手勢。<br />\n<br />\nDarlette接受傳媒訪問時表示，「沒想過會在這裏見到他，他真的好sweet，最好的人，他一身鐵騎士打扮，正在喝東西，當我們上前打擾他，他仍表現親切」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，奇洛李維斯今年與婚禮有緣，他伙拍《怪奇物語》雲露娜維達（Winona Ryder）主演的中年人愛情片《婚禮進行識》（Destination Wedding），剛剛在美國限定戲院上映，香港觀衆則要等到10月才有機會欣賞。該片講述奇洛飾演毒舌寡佬，要去出席旅行婚禮，在機場撞正同樣毒舌的熟女雲露娜維達，兩人火星撞地球，命運卻安排他倆參加同一個婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180905/s00007/1536081361542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180905%2Fs00007%2F1536081361542&d=vlUG29c%2FDcun%2FsoclCinnywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6580390c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180905%2Fs00007%2F1536081361542&h=cecbcb11\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180905/s00007/1536081361542</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/da84cbadd44c3c0edcf40ee712607065/5C29B446/t51.2885-15/e35/39943296_1158586370983932_1189828316335424095_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2Fda84cbadd44c3c0edcf40ee712607065%2F5C29B446%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F39943296_1158586370983932_1189828316335424095_n.jpg&h=c9b9f813&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eecee599aaec37d9488f58ea6696377fbe595082","tid":827853,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"靚仔毒撚"},{"pid":"adb0796eed4dce7ce3efd2b2578d34dc7253c505","tid":827853,"uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"睇人開心自己都可以開心下"},{"pid":"432a6dfd6cdd1ed72f260bf2825dda1b79d99615","tid":827853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1af2b8a0daf2d519fd90a5bdd643a80df95a13e","tid":827853,"uid":73443,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"點解一有佢就一定出第一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁講件事唔得咩"},{"pid":"f10cabdf88ef921ae21d50a9c56f3c0045d760c3","tid":827853,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f1af2b8a0daf2d519fd90a5bdd643a80df95a13e","tid":827853,"uid":73443,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"點解一有佢就一定出第一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁講件事唔得咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"唔講成件事出嚟，咁同阿bob同新人影相有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b11f398a5976edf83738d1c41fd09391150b02","tid":827853,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"連奇洛李維斯都要做錯rock嘅手勢"},{"pid":"72233e2de5ad87cd4cf5b8da2e4fc4440713bc35","tid":827853,"uid":7050,"like":0,"